# #---Workspace Bindings---# #---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Requires on pulseaudio. TODO: also change workspace on other monitors?
# Disables all sound, mutes microphone, moves to a new workspace and opens innocent looking programs
#-----------

#bindsym $mod+Tab		workspace back_and_forth
#bindsym $mod+semicolon		workspace next
#bindsym $mod+backslash		workspace back_and_forth

